jdbcQuery.query: SELECT STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.PER_ID, STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_TYPE, STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_DATE, STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.RFD_CAL_DAY_CODE_ID, STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_PERIOD_ID, CASE WHEN STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_TYPE = 'ABS' THEN RFD_STUDENT_ABSENCE_REASON.RFD_STU_ABS_REASON_CODE ELSE RFD_STUDENT_TARDY_REASON.RFD_STU_TARDY_REASON_CODE END REASON, CASE WHEN STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_TYPE = 'ABS' THEN RFD_STUDENT_ABSENCE_REASON.RFD_STU_ABS_REASON_DESC ELSE RFD_STUDENT_TARDY_REASON.RFD_STU_TARDY_REASON_DESC END REASON_DESC, CASE WHEN STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_TYPE = 'ABS' THEN RFD_STUDENT_ABSENCE_REASON.RFS_STU_ABS_REASON_EXCUSED ELSE RFD_STUDENT_TARDY_REASON.RFD_STU_TARDY_REASON_EXCUSED END REASON_EXCUSED, CASE WHEN STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_TYPE = 'ABS' THEN RFD_STUDENT_ABSENCE_REASON.RFD_STU_ABS_REASON_STATE_REP ELSE 'N' END STATE_REPORTED, STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_IS_SIG, STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_GRADE_GROUP , STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_COURSE_ID, STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_SECTION_ID, STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.LOC_ID, STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.STUDENT_CAL_ID FROM STUDENT_ATTENDANCE JOIN STUDENT_ENROLLMENT ON STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.PER_ID = STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.PER_ID AND STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_FISCAL_YEAR = STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.STU_ENR_FISCAL_YEAR AND STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_LOC_ID = STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.LOC_ID AND STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_DATE BETWEEN STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.STU_ENR_ENTRY_DATE AND COALESCE(STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.STU_ENRLAST_ENROLLED_DATE, STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_DATE) JOIN STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE ON STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_FISCAL_YEAR = STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR AND STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_LOC_ID = STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.LOC_ID AND STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.STUDENT_CAL_ID = STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.STUDENT_CAL_ID AND STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_DATE = STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.STUDENT_CAL_DATE LEFT JOIN RFD_STUDENT_ABSENCE_REASON ON STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.RFD_STU_ABS_REASON_CODE = RFD_STUDENT_ABSENCE_REASON.RFD_STU_ABS_REASON_CODE AND STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_TYPE = 'ABS' LEFT JOIN RFD_STUDENT_TARDY_REASON ON STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.RFD_STU_TARDY_REASON_CODE = RFD_STUDENT_TARDY_REASON.RFD_STU_TARDY_REASON_CODE AND STUDENT_ATTENDANCE.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_TYPE = 'TDY' WHERE STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.STU_ENR_FISCAL_YEAR = (SELECT BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_VALUE FROM BUSINESS_RULE_PARAMETER WHERE BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_NAME = 'Fiscal Year' AND BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_PARAM = 'Current Fiscal Year')

SELECT SC.STU_PER_ID, SC.CONTACT_PER_ID, SC.STU_CONTACT_TYPE, SC.RFD_RELATIONSHIP_CODE, GP.PER_FIRST_NAME, GP.PER_LAST_NAME, MA.ADDR_LINE1 MAILING_ADDR_LINE1, MA.ADDR_LINE2 MAILING_ADDR_LINE2, MA.ADDR_CITY MAILING_CITY, MA.ADDR_STATE MAILING_STATE, MA.ADDR_ZIP MAILING_ZIP, HA.ADDR_LINE1 HOME_ADDR_LINE1, HA.ADDR_LINE2 HOME_ADDR_LINE2, HA.ADDR_CITY HOME_CITY, HA.ADDR_STATE HOME_STATE, HA.ADDR_ZIP HOME_ZIP, CP.PHONE_AREA_CODE CELL_AREA_CODE, CP.PHONE_EXCHANGE CELL_EXCHANGE, CP.PHONE_NUMBER CELL_NUMBER, HP.PHONE_AREA_CODE HOME_AREA_CODE, HP.PHONE_EXCHANGE HOME_EXCHANGE, HP.PHONE_NUMBER HOME_NUMBER, EA.EMAIL_ADDRESS, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY SC.STU_PER_ID ORDER BY SC.STU_CONTACT_PRIORITY, SC.CONTACT_PER_ID) PG_PRIORITY_ORDER FROM STUDENT_CONTACT SC LEFT JOIN PERSON GP ON SC.CONTACT_PER_ID = GP.PER_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PA.PER_ID, MADDR.*, Row_Number() Over(Partition BY PA.PER_ID ORDER BY MADDR.RFS_ADDR_CODE DESC, MADDR.ADDR_ID) RNUMB FROM PERSON_ADDRESS PA INNER JOIN ADDRESS AS MADDR ON PA.ADDR_ID = MADDR.ADDR_ID AND MADDR.RFS_ADDR_CODE IN ('Mailing', 'Home')) AS MA ON SC.CONTACT_PER_ID = MA.PER_ID AND MA.RNUMB = 1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PA.PER_ID, HADDR.*, Row_Number() Over(Partition BY PA.PER_ID ORDER BY HADDR.ADDR_ID) RNUMB FROM PERSON_ADDRESS PA INNER JOIN ADDRESS AS HADDR ON PA.ADDR_ID = HADDR.ADDR_ID AND HADDR.RFS_ADDR_CODE = 'Home') AS HA ON SC.CONTACT_PER_ID = HA.PER_ID AND HA.RNUMB = 1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PP.PER_ID, CPHN.*, Row_Number() Over(Partition BY PP.PER_ID ORDER BY CPHN.PHONE_ID) RNUMB FROM PERSON_PHONE PP INNER JOIN PHONE AS CPHN ON PP.PHONE_ID = CPHN.PHONE_ID AND CPHN.RFS_PHONE_CODE = 'Cell') AS CP ON SC.CONTACT_PER_ID = CP.PER_ID AND CP.RNUMB = 1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PP.PER_ID, HPHN.*, Row_Number() Over(Partition BY PP.PER_ID ORDER BY HPHN.PHONE_ID) RNUMB FROM PERSON_PHONE PP INNER JOIN PHONE HPHN ON PP.PHONE_ID = HPHN.PHONE_ID AND HPHN.RFS_PHONE_CODE = 'Home') AS HP ON SC.CONTACT_PER_ID = HP.PER_ID AND HP.RNUMB = 1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PE.PER_ID, EADDR.*, Row_Number() Over(Partition BY PE.PER_ID ORDER BY EADDR.RFS_EMAIL_CODE DESC, EADDR.EMAIL_ID) RNUMB FROM PERSON_EMAIL PE INNER JOIN EMAIL AS EADDR ON PE.EMAIL_ID = EADDR.EMAIL_ID) AS EA ON SC.CONTACT_PER_ID = EA.PER_ID AND EA.RNUMB = 1 WHERE SC.STU_CONTACT_TYPE IN ('Parent', 'Guardian') AND SC.STU_CONTACT_STUDENT_LIVES_WITH = 'Y'

SELECT P.PER_ID, CASE WHEN P.PER_LATINO_FLG IS NOT NULL AND P.PER_LATINO_FLG = 'Y' THEN 'Hispanic/Latino' WHEN COUNT(PR.RFS_RACE_NAME) = 1 THEN MAX(PR.RFS_RACE_NAME) WHEN COUNT(PR.RFS_RACE_NAME) = 0 THEN NULL ELSE 'Two or more races' END RACE FROM PERSON P LEFT OUTER JOIN PERSON_RACE PR ON P.PER_ID = PR.PER_ID AND PR.RFS_RACE_NAME IN ('American Indian or Alaska Native', 'Asian', 'Black or African American', 'Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander', 'White') GROUP BY P.PER_ID, P.PER_LATINO_FLG

Select X.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM, X.PER_ID, X.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE EFF_DATE, Coalesce(X.EXIT_DATE,{ts '9999-12-31 00:00:00'}) EXIT_DATE, X.STU_DT_TRK_VALUE, X.STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG from (select STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.*, SDTVEXIT.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE EXIT_DATE, Row_Number() Over(Partition By STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.PER_ID, STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM, STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE Order By SDTVEXIT.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE) RNUMB from STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE Left Join STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE SDTVEXIT On STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.PER_ID = SDTVEXIT.PER_ID And STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = SDTVEXIT.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM And STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE < SDTVEXIT.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE Where STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE < Current_Timestamp) X Where X.RNUMB = 1 And X.STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' And X.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM <> 'Career and Technology Indicator'

Select PER_ID, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = '4 Year Plan' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Four_Year_Plan, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = '504 Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Indicator_504, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'At-Risk Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As At_Risk_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Attribution Code' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Attribution_Code, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Bilingual Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Bilingual_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Bilingual Summer School Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Bilingual_Summer_Sch, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Campus ID of Residence' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Campus_ID_of_Residence, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Day Care Support Services' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Day_Care_Support_Serv, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Displaced Homemaker' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Displaced_Homemaker, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'District of RDSPD Service' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As District_of_RDSPD, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Dyslexia Indicator Code' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Dyslexia_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Early Childhood Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Early_Childhood_Indic, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Early Reading Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Early_Reading_Indic, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Economic Disadvantage 1 Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Economic_Disadvantag1, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Economic Disadvantage 2 Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Economic_Disadvantag2, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'ESL Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As ESL_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Even Start Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Even_Start_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Exclude Student from Ranking' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Exclude_Student_from_Ranking, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Gifted and Talented Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Gifted_and_Talented, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'IEP on Record' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As IEP_on_Record, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Immigrant Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Immigrant_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Instructional Setting' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Instructional_Settin, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Interpreting Service Type' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Interpreting_Service, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Interrupted Formal Education' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Interrupted_Formal_Ed, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'LEP Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As LEP_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Migrant Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Migrant_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Multiply Disabled Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Multiply_Disabled_Indic, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Parental Permission' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Parental_Permission, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'PEP Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As PEP_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'PPCD Service Location' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As PPCD_Service_Loc, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Preschool Program for Children with Disabilities' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As PPCD, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Primary Disability' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Primary_Disability, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'PRS Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As PRS_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Regional Day School Program for Deaf' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As RDSPD, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Secondary Disability' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Secondary_Disability, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Single Parent Pregnant Teen' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Single_Parent_Preg_Teen, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Special Ed Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Special_Ed_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Speech Therapy Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Speech_Therapy, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'SSI Promotion Retention Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As SSI_Promotion_Retent, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Student Crisis' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Student_Crisis, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Tertiary Disability' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Tertiary_Disability, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Title I Indicator' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Title_I_Indicator, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Transportation Support Services' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Transp_Support_serv, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'UnSchooled-Asylee/Refugee' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As UnSchooled_Asylee_Ref, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Work Study Support Services' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Work_Study_Support_Serv, Max(Case When RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Years in U.S Schools' And STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N' Then STU_DT_TRK_VALUE End) As Years_in_US_Schools From (Select STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.*, Row_Number() Over(Partition By STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM, STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.PER_ID Order By STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE Desc) RNUMB From STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE Where STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE <= Current_Timestamp) SDTV Where RNUMB = 1 Group By PER_ID

SELECT SSC.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM, SSC.PER_ID, SSC.RFS_GRADE_CODE, P.PER_GENDER, SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR, SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_ACTION_DT, SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_TSTD_COR_FLG, RSLT.RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT_NM, RSLT.RFS_P_SCREENING_RESULT_CD, FLW.RFD_SCREENING_FLLWP_NM, FLW.RFS_P_SCREENING_FLLWP_CD, DIAG.RFD_SCREENING_DIAGNOSIS_NM, DIAG.RFS_P_SCREENING_DIAG_CD, COALESCE( ( SELECT DISTINCT 'Y' FROM STUDENT_SCREENING SSRS LEFT JOIN RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT RSLTRS ON SSRS.RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT_NM = RSLTRS.RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT_NM WHERE SSRS.PER_ID = SSC.PER_ID AND SSRS.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM =SSC.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM AND SSRS.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR = SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR AND RSLTRS.RFS_P_SCREENING_RESULT_CD = 'RS' AND SSRS.STUDENT_SCREENING_ID <> SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_ID),'N') AS Has_Different_Rescreen FROM STUDENT_SCREENING SSC INNER JOIN (SELECT BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_VALUE AS STUDENT_FY FROM BUSINESS_RULE_PARAMETER WHERE BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_NAME = 'Fiscal Year' AND BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_PARAM = 'Current Fiscal Year') ON STUDENT_FY - 1 <= SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR JOIN PERSON P ON SSC.PER_ID = P.PER_ID LEFT JOIN RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT RSLT ON SSC.RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT_NM = RSLT.RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT_NM AND SSC.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM = RSLT.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM LEFT JOIN RFD_SCREENING_ACTION_FOLLOW_UP FLW ON SSC.RFD_SCREENING_FLLWP_NM = FLW.RFD_SCREENING_FLLWP_NM AND SSC.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM = FLW.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM LEFT JOIN RFD_SCREENING_DIAGNOSIS DIAG ON SSC.RFD_SCREENING_DIAGNOSIS_NM = DIAG.RFD_SCREENING_DIAGNOSIS_NM WHERE SSC.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM = 'Spinal' AND (( SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR = STUDENT_FY AND RSLT.RFS_P_SCREENING_RESULT_CD IN ('PT', 'RS', 'RF', 'P')) OR ( SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR = (STUDENT_FY - 1) AND RSLT.RFS_P_SCREENING_RESULT_CD IN ('RF') AND ( FLW.RFS_P_SCREENING_FLLWP_CD IN ('LOB', 'LBR', 'LSG', 'LO') OR DIAG.RFS_P_SCREENING_DIAG_CD IN ('LSC', 'LKY', 'LO', 'LNOR')))) AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM STUDENT_SCREENING SSC2 JOIN RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT RSLT2 ON SSC2.RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT_NM = RSLT2.RFDS_SCREENING_RESULT_NM AND SSC2.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM = RSLT2.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM LEFT JOIN RFD_SCREENING_ACTION_FOLLOW_UP FLW2 ON SSC2.RFD_SCREENING_FLLWP_NM = FLW2.RFD_SCREENING_FLLWP_NM AND SSC2.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM = FLW2.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM LEFT JOIN RFD_SCREENING_DIAGNOSIS DIAG2 ON SSC2.RFD_SCREENING_DIAGNOSIS_NM = DIAG2.RFD_SCREENING_DIAGNOSIS_NM WHERE SSC2.PER_ID = SSC.PER_ID AND SSC2.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM = SSC.RFS_STUDENT_SCREENING_NM AND SSC2.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR = SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR AND (( SSC2.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR = SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR AND RSLT2.RFS_P_SCREENING_RESULT_CD IN ('PT', 'RS', 'RF', 'P')) OR ( SSC2.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR = SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_FISCAL_YR AND RSLT2.RFS_P_SCREENING_RESULT_CD IN ('RF') AND ( FLW2.RFS_P_SCREENING_FLLWP_CD IN ('LOB', 'LBR', 'LSG', 'LO') OR DIAG2.RFS_P_SCREENING_DIAG_CD IN ('LSC', 'LKY', 'LO', 'LNOR')))) AND ( SSC2.STUDENT_SCREENING_ACTION_DT > SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_ACTION_DT OR ( SSC2.STUDENT_SCREENING_ACTION_DT = SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_ACTION_DT AND SSC2.STUDENT_SCREENING_ID < SSC.STUDENT_SCREENING_ID)))

SELECT G.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR, G.PER_ID, G.STU_GRD_GROUP_ID, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 1 THEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_LABEL END) CYCLE_1_LABEL, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 1 THEN G.STU_GRD_TYP_GRP_SEC_V_VCGRDVAL END) CYCLE_1_GRADE, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 2 THEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_LABEL END ) CYCLE_2_LABEL, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 2 THEN G.STU_GRD_TYP_GRP_SEC_V_VCGRDVAL END) CYCLE_2_GRADE, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 3 THEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_LABEL END) CYCLE_3_LABEL, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 3 THEN G.STU_GRD_TYP_GRP_SEC_V_VCGRDVAL END) CYCLE_3_GRADE, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 4 THEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_LABEL END ) CYCLE_4_LABEL, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 4 THEN G.STU_GRD_TYP_GRP_SEC_V_VCGRDVAL END) CYCLE_4_GRADE, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 5 THEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_LABEL END) CYCLE_5_LABEL, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 5 THEN G.STU_GRD_TYP_GRP_SEC_V_VCGRDVAL END) CYCLE_5_GRADE, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 6 THEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_LABEL END ) CYCLE_6_LABEL, MAX( CASE WHEN CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE = 6 THEN G.STU_GRD_TYP_GRP_SEC_V_VCGRDVAL END) CYCLE_6_GRADE FROM STUDENT_GRD_TYP_GRP_SEC_VAL G JOIN (SELECT BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_VALUE AS STUDENT_FY FROM BUSINESS_RULE_PARAMETER WHERE BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_NAME = 'Fiscal Year' AND BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_PARAM = 'Current Fiscal Year') YR ON G.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR = YR.STUDENT_FY JOIN CAMPUS_GRADE_TYPE CGT ON G.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR = CGT.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR AND G.LOC_ID = CGT.LOC_ID AND G.STUDENT_CAL_ID = CGT.STUDENT_CAL_ID AND G.GRADE_TYPE_NM = CGT.GRADE_TYPE_NM WHERE CGT.GRADE_TYPE_CATEGORY = 'Report Card' AND CGT.GRADE_TYPE_GB_CYCLE IS NOT NULL GROUP BY G.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR, G.PER_ID, G.STU_GRD_GROUP_ID

Select SDTV.PER_ID, SDTV.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM, SDTV.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE FROM ( SELECT STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.*, Row_Number() Over(Partition BY STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM, STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.PER_ID ORDER BY STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE DESC) RNUMB FROM STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE JOIN RFDS_DATE_TRACK_FIELD ON STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = RFDS_DATE_TRACK_FIELD.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM WHERE STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE <= CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AND RFDS_DATE_TRACK_FIELD.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_CAT_NM = 'District Program') SDTV WHERE SDTV.RNUMB = 1 AND SDTV.STU_DT_TRK_END_PROG_FLG = 'N'

Select SE.PER_ID, SE.LOC_ID From (select STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.PER_ID, STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.LOC_ID, Row_Number() Over(Partition By STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.PER_ID Order By STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.STU_ENR_ENTRY_DATE Desc) RNUMB From STUDENT_ENROLLMENT Where STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.STU_ENR_STATUS In ('E','W')) SE Where SE.RNUMB = 1

Select SE.STU_ENR_FISCAL_YEAR, SRR.PER_ID, Coalesce(SRR.STU_RSTRNT_LOC_ID, SE.LOC_ID) RESTRAINT_LOC_ID, SRR.STU_RSTRNT_RSN_DT As RESTRAINT_DT, SRR.STU_RSTRNT_RSN_SEQ As RESTRAINT_SEQ, SRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_STAFF_TYP_NM, SRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_TYP_NM, RRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_REASON_LBL, RRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_REASON_NM, Max(Case When SDTV.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Primary Disability' Then DIS.RFD_DISABILITY_LBL End) As Prim_Disability, Max(Case When SDTV.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Secondary Disability' Then DIS.RFD_DISABILITY_LBL End) As Sec_Disability, Max(Case When SDTV.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = 'Tertiary Disability' Then DIS.RFD_DISABILITY_LBL End) As Tert_Disability From STUDENT_RESTRAINT_REASON SRR Left Join STUDENT_ENROLLMENT SE On SRR.PER_ID = SE.PER_ID And SRR.STU_RSTRNT_RSN_DT >= SE.STU_ENR_ENTRY_DATE And (SE.STU_ENR_EXIT_DATE Is Null Or SE.STU_ENR_EXIT_DATE > SRR.STU_RSTRNT_RSN_DT) Join RFD_RESTRAINT_REASON RRR On SRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_REASON_NM = RRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_REASON_NM Left Join STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE SDTV On RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM In ('Primary Disability','Secondary Disability', 'Tertiary Disability') And SRR.PER_ID = SDTV.PER_ID And SDTV.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE <= SRR.STU_RSTRNT_RSN_DT Left Join RFD_DISABILITY DIS On SDTV.STU_DT_TRK_VALUE = DIS.RFD_DISABILITY_NM Where Not Exists (Select * From STUDENT_DATE_TRACKED_VALUE SDTV2 Where STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE <= SRR.STU_RSTRNT_RSN_DT And STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE > SDTV.STU_DT_TRK_EFF_DATE And PER_ID = SDTV.PER_ID And RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM = SDTV.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM) Group By SE.STU_ENR_FISCAL_YEAR, SRR.STU_RSTRNT_RSN_DT, SRR.STU_RSTRNT_RSN_SEQ, SRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_STAFF_TYP_NM, SRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_TYP_NM, RRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_REASON_LBL, RRR.RFD_RESTRAINT_REASON_NM, Coalesce(SRR.STU_RSTRNT_LOC_ID, SE.LOC_ID), SRR.PER_ID

SELECT SC.PER_ID, SC.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR, SC.LOC_ID LOC_ID, SC.STUDENT_CAL_ID, SC.DIST_COURSE_ID, SC.STU_GRD_GROUP_ID, DCC.DIST_COURSE_LONG_DESC, SC.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID, SC.STUDENT_CAL_TERM_TYPE, LTP.RFD_CAL_DAY_CODE_ID, LTP.STU_CAL_PERIOD_ID, CASE WHEN SCP.STU_CAL_PERIOD_SPECIAL_DESG = 'Homeroom' OR DCC.DIST_COURSE_IS_HOMEROOM_FLG = 'Y' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END IS_HOMEROOM, SC.STU_CLASS_ENTER_DATE, SC.STU_CLASS_EXIT_DATE, COALESCE(LCSC.PARENT_DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR, SC.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR) T_FISCAL_YEAR, COALESCE(LCSC.PARENT_LOC_ID, SC.LOC_ID) T_LOC_ID, COALESCE(LCSC.PARENT_CAL_ID, SC.STUDENT_CAL_ID) T_STUDENT_CAL_ID, COALESCE(LCSC.PARENT_DIST_COURSE_ID, SC.DIST_COURSE_ID) T_DIST_COURSE_ID, COALESCE(LCSC.PARENT_LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID, SC.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID) T_LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID FROM STUDENT_COURSE_REQUEST CR JOIN (SELECT BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_VALUE AS STUDENT_FY FROM BUSINESS_RULE_PARAMETER WHERE BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_NAME = 'Fiscal Year' AND BUS_RULE_PARAM_RULE_PARAM = 'Current Fiscal Year') YR ON CR.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR = YR.STUDENT_FY JOIN STUDENT_CLASS SC ON CR.STUDENT_CRS_REQ_ID = SC.STUDENT_CRS_REQ_ID INNER JOIN LOCATION_COURSE_SECTION LCS ON SC.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID = LCS.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID AND SC.LOC_ID = LCS.LOC_ID AND SC.DIST_COURSE_ID = LCS.DIST_COURSE_ID AND SC.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR = LCS.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR AND SC.STUDENT_CAL_ID = LCS.STUDENT_CAL_ID INNER JOIN LOCATION_CRS_SEC_TERM_PERIOD LTP ON LCS.LOC_ID = LTP.LOC_ID AND LCS.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR = LTP.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR AND LCS.STUDENT_CAL_ID = LTP.STUDENT_CAL_ID AND LCS.DIST_COURSE_ID = LTP.DIST_COURSE_ID AND LCS.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID = LTP.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID AND SC.STUDENT_CAL_TERM_TYPE = LTP.STUDENT_CAL_TERM_TYPE INNER JOIN STUDENT_CALENDAR_TERM TRM ON SC.LOC_ID = TRM.LOC_ID AND SC.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR = TRM.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR AND SC.STUDENT_CAL_ID = TRM.STUDENT_CAL_ID AND SC.STUDENT_CAL_TERM_TYPE = TRM.STUDENT_CAL_TERM_TYPE INNER JOIN DISTRICT_COURSE_CATALOG DCC ON LCS.DIST_COURSE_ID = DCC.DIST_COURSE_ID AND LCS.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR = DCC.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR INNER JOIN STUDENT_CALENDAR_PERIOD SCP ON LTP.LOC_ID = SCP.LOC_ID AND LTP.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR = SCP.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR AND LTP.STUDENT_CAL_ID = SCP.STUDENT_CAL_ID AND LTP.RFD_CAL_DAY_CODE_ID = SCP.RFD_CAL_DAY_CODE_ID AND LTP.STU_CAL_PERIOD_ID = SCP.STU_CAL_PERIOD_ID LEFT JOIN LOCATION_CRS_SEC_CONNECTION LCSC ON SC.DIST_COURSE_ID = LCSC.CHILD_DIST_COURSE_ID AND SC.LOC_ID= LCSC.CHILD_LOC_ID AND SC.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID = LCSC.CHILD_CRS_SECTION_ID AND SC.STUDENT_CAL_ID = LCSC.CHILD_CAL_ID AND SC.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR = LCSC.CHILD_DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR AND LCSC.LOC_CRS_SEC_CONNECT_TYPE != 'Attendance' WHERE ( SC.STU_CLASS_EXIT_DATE = TRM.STUDENT_CAL_TERM_END_DATE)

Select STH.PER_ID, STH.RFS_MONTH_OF_YEAR_NM, STH.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_CAL_YR, STH.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_COUNTY_NUMBER, STH.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_DIST_NUMBER, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_ID, STD.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_ID, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_FISCAL_YR, STD.RFD_GPA_LEVEL_NM, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CALENDAR_ID, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CAMPUS_ID, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CAMPUS_ENR, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CAMP_TERM, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CREDIT_ATMPT, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CREDIT_EARNED, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CREDIT_TYPE, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CRS_ID, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_SECTION_ID, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_DIST_LEARN, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_DUAL_CREDIT, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_FINAL_AVG_GRD, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_GPA_COUNTER, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_GRAD_REQ_CAT, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_GRD_TYPE_NM, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_GROUP_SEQ, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_MAN_EDIT_FLG, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_ORGIN, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_PART_OF_CRS, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_PRINT_CAT, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_SERVICE_ID_CD, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_STU_GRD_LVL, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_SVC_ID_DES_OVD, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_415_PF_NM, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_GRD_GROUP_ID, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_GRD_VALUE, STD.RFD_EXCSSV_ABS_CODE_ID, STD.RFD_DIST_CRS_CAT_NM, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_ATC_CD, STD.RFD_CRD_APPL_CD, STD.RFS_P_NON_CAMP_INSTR_CD, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_STU_BEGIN_DT, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_STU_END_DT, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_CLASS_ID, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_GP_OVRRD_FLG, STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_EMP_PER_ID, STD.RFS_P_CRS_SEQUENCE_CD, STD.STU_TRSCRIPT_DET_COMMENT, STD.STU_TRSCRIPT_DET_CLLG_CRD_ERND, STD.STD_JJAEP_HM_CMPS_LOC_ID, AARS.AAR From STUDENT_TRANSCRIPT_HDR STH Join STUDENT_TRANSCRIPT_DETAIL STD On STD.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_ID = STH.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_ID Join (Select X.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_ID, X.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_ID, concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 1 Then X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID End), concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 2 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End), concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 3 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End), concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 4 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End), concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 5 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End), concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 6 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End), concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 7 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End), concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 8 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End), concat(Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 9 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End), Max(Case When X.RNUMB = 10 Then concat(' ',X.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) Else '' End)))))))))) AAR From (Select STUDENT_TRANSCRIPT_DET_AAR_PRG.*, Row_Number() Over(Partition By STUDENT_TRANSCRIPT_DET_AAR_PRG.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_ID, STUDENT_TRANSCRIPT_DET_AAR_PRG.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_ID Order By STUDENT_TRANSCRIPT_DET_AAR_PRG.RFD_AAR_PROG_CODE_ID) RNUMB From STUDENT_TRANSCRIPT_DET_AAR_PRG) X Group By X.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_ID, X.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_ID) AARS On STD.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_ID = AARS.STU_TRSCRIPT_HDR_ID And STD.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_ID = AARS.STU_TRSCRPT_DET_ID

joinedDataSetRef.joinString: join TEAMS_STUDENT_ENROLLMENT TEAMS_STUDENT_ENROLLMENT on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == TEAMS_STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.PER_ID)
join TEAMS_PERSON TEAMS_PERSON on (TEAMS_PERSON.PER_ID == TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID)
left outer join Parent_Guardian_Info Parent_Guardian_Info on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Parent_Guardian_Info.STU_PER_ID)
join TEAMS_LOCATION TEAMS_LOCATION on (TEAMS_LOCATION.LOC_ID == TEAMS_STUDENT_ENROLLMENT.LOC_ID)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_STUDENT_COHORT TEAMS_RFD_STUDENT_COHORT on (TEAMS_STUDENT.RFD_STUDENT_COHORT_NM == TEAMS_RFD_STUDENT_COHORT.RFD_STUDENT_COHORT_NM)
left outer join Special_Programs_Basic Special_Programs_Basic on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Special_Programs_Basic.PER_ID)
left outer join Student_Schedule Student_Schedule on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Student_Schedule.PER_ID)
left outer join Current_Year_Attendance Current_Year_Attendance on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Current_Year_Attendance.PER_ID)
left outer join Race_Ethnicity Race_Ethnicity on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Race_Ethnicity.PER_ID)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_ECONOMIC_DISADVANTAGE TEAMS_RFD_ECONOMIC_DISADVANTAGE on (Special_Programs_Basic.ECONOMIC_DISADVANTAG1 == TEAMS_RFD_ECONOMIC_DISADVANTAGE.RFD_ECON_DIS_ADVNTG_NM)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_ECONOMIC_DISADVANTAGE2 TEAMS_RFD_ECONOMIC_DISADVANTAGE2 on (Special_Programs_Basic.ECONOMIC_DISADVANTAG2 == TEAMS_RFD_ECONOMIC_DISADVANTAGE2.RFD_ECON_DIS_ADVNTG_NM)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_PARTICIPATE_CODEATRISK TEAMS_RFD_PARTICIPATE_CODEATRISK on (Special_Programs_Basic.AT_RISK_INDICATOR == TEAMS_RFD_PARTICIPATE_CODEATRISK.RFD_PARTICIPATE_CD_CODE)
left outer join Student_Retraints Student_Retraints on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Student_Retraints.PER_ID)
left outer join Student_District_Programs Student_District_Programs on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Student_District_Programs.PER_ID)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_GENERATION TEAMS_RFD_GENERATION on (TEAMS_PERSON.RFD_GENERATION_CODE == TEAMS_RFD_GENERATION.RFD_GENERATION_CODE)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_GRADUATION_PLAN TEAMS_RFD_GRADUATION_PLAN on (TEAMS_STUDENT.RFD_GRADUATION_PLAN_CODE == TEAMS_RFD_GRADUATION_PLAN.RFD_GRADUATION_PLAN_CODE)
left outer join TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER.PER_ID)

left outer join TEAMS_DSCP_INCIDENT TEAMS_DSCP_INCIDENT on (TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER.DSCP_INCIDENT_FID == TEAMS_DSCP_INCIDENT.DSCP_INCIDENT_FID and TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER.DSCP_INCIDENT_FISCAL_YR == TEAMS_DSCP_INCIDENT.DSCP_INCIDENT_FISCAL_YR)

left outer join TEAMS_DSCP_ACTION_TAKEN TEAMS_DSCP_ACTION_TAKEN on (TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER.DSCP_INCIDENT_FID == TEAMS_DSCP_ACTION_TAKEN.DSCP_INCIDENT_FID and TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER.DSCP_INCIDENT_FISCAL_YR == TEAMS_DSCP_ACTION_TAKEN.DSCP_INCIDENT_FISCAL_YR and TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER.RFD_DSCP_OFFENSE_NM == TEAMS_DSCP_ACTION_TAKEN.RFD_DSCP_OFFENSE_NM)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_LEN_DIFF_REASON TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_LEN_DIFF_REASON on (TEAMS_DSCP_ACTION_TAKEN.RFD_DSCP_LEN_DIFF_REASON_NM == TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_LEN_DIFF_REASON.RFD_DSCP_LEN_DIFF_REASON_NM)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_OFFENSE TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_OFFENSE on (TEAMS_DSCP_OFFENDER.RFD_DSCP_OFFENSE_NM == TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_OFFENSE.RFD_DSCP_OFFENSE_NM)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_ACTION TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_ACTION on (TEAMS_DSCP_ACTION_TAKEN.RFD_DSCP_ACTION_NM == TEAMS_RFD_DSCP_ACTION.RFD_DSCP_ACTION_NM)
join Student_Ownership_Campus Student_Ownership_Campus on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Student_Ownership_Campus.PER_ID)
left outer join Special_and_District_Programs_History Special_and_District_Programs_History on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Special_and_District_Programs_History.PER_ID)
join TEAMS_RFDS_DATE_TRACK_FIELD TEAMS_RFDS_DATE_TRACK_FIELD on (TEAMS_RFDS_DATE_TRACK_FIELD.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM == Special_and_District_Programs_History.RFDS_DT_TRACK_FIELD_NM)
left outer join TEAMS_RFD_PARTICIPATE_CODEGT TEAMS_RFD_PARTICIPATE_CODEGT on (Special_Programs_Basic.GIFTED_AND_TALENTED == TEAMS_RFD_PARTICIPATE_CODEGT.RFD_PARTICIPATE_CD_CODE)
left outer join Student_Transcripts Student_Transcripts on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Student_Transcripts.PER_ID)

join STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE on (Current_Year_Attendance.LOC_ID == STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.LOC_ID and Current_Year_Attendance.STUDENT_CAL_ID == STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.STUDENT_CAL_ID and Current_Year_Attendance.STUDENT_ATTENDANCE_DATE == STUDENT_CALENDAR_DATE.STUDENT_CAL_DATE)

left outer join V_SEC_CURRENT_TEACHER V_SEC_CURRENT_TEACHER on (Student_Schedule.T_FISCAL_YEAR == V_SEC_CURRENT_TEACHER.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR and Student_Schedule.T_DIST_COURSE_ID == V_SEC_CURRENT_TEACHER.DIST_COURSE_ID and Student_Schedule.T_LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID == V_SEC_CURRENT_TEACHER.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID and Student_Schedule.T_LOC_ID == V_SEC_CURRENT_TEACHER.LOC_ID and Student_Schedule.T_STUDENT_CAL_ID == V_SEC_CURRENT_TEACHER.STUDENT_CAL_ID)

join LOCATION_COURSE_SECTION LOCATION_COURSE_SECTION on (Student_Schedule.T_FISCAL_YEAR == LOCATION_COURSE_SECTION.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR and Student_Schedule.T_DIST_COURSE_ID == LOCATION_COURSE_SECTION.DIST_COURSE_ID and Student_Schedule.T_LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID == LOCATION_COURSE_SECTION.LOC_CRS_SECTION_ID and Student_Schedule.T_LOC_ID == LOCATION_COURSE_SECTION.LOC_ID and Student_Schedule.T_STUDENT_CAL_ID == LOCATION_COURSE_SECTION.STUDENT_CAL_ID)
join TEAMS_LOCATION1_TAUGHT TEAMS_LOCATION1_TAUGHT on (Student_Schedule.T_LOC_ID == TEAMS_LOCATION1_TAUGHT.LOC_ID)

left outer join Student_Cycle_Grade Student_Cycle_Grade on (Student_Schedule.PER_ID == Student_Cycle_Grade.PER_ID and Student_Schedule.STU_GRD_GROUP_ID == Student_Cycle_Grade.STU_GRD_GROUP_ID and Student_Schedule.DIST_COURSE_FISCAL_YEAR == Student_Cycle_Grade.STUDENT_CAL_FISCAL_YEAR)
left outer join Spinal_Screening Spinal_Screening on (TEAMS_STUDENT.PER_ID == Spinal_Screening.PER_ID)
